ng part of the reason why I have prospered." "I am a proud graduate of Bradford, and all others whom also attended should also be more than proud of their attendance there. Thank you again, and God Bless you. one of my other roommates was Japanese chap, and his father was some kind of high political ruler of the country at the time. Thinking back on all this makes me proud of having been affiliated with Bradford College. Thank you.', 8422, 0), (34472, 'Dare to blaze.', 8510, 0), (34473, 'When we set expectations and nourish them with appreciation, we will get better results.', 2586, 0), (34474, 'Life is beautiful so it encourages me to smile. I smile at life to make it beautiful.', 2586, 0), (34475, 'Do what supports your long-term goals not what is easier.', 2586, 0), (34476, 'The greatest duty of life is to find the ultimate purpose of life. The second greatest duty is to put a laser focus on it and take action.', 2586, 0), (34477, 'I search for love frantically... and quitting at the last moment by making excuse for myself that I''ve tried', 8549, 0), (34478, 'Accept the challenge and never fear to change.', 2586, 0), (34479, 'What other people think is important to them. What you think has great importance to you.', 2586, 0), (34480, 'The greatest obstacle to success is the fear of failure.', 2586, 0), (34481, 'Our eyes are as open as much our minds are.', 2586, 0), (34482, 'To win, expect to win. Expectations create reality.', 2586, 0), (34483, 'The only person you should compete with is you.', 2586, 0), (34484, 'Never forget to smile', 8550, 0), (34485, 'What you love will live in your heart and grow.', 2586, 0), (34486, 'Even if you cover the whole world with darkness, you can never stop the sun from rising.', 2586, 0), (34487, 'True love is not in possessions or obsessions', 8551, 0), (34488, 'If you wait until you are ready, you will keep waiting forever.', 5102, 0), (34489, 'Great minds find beauties and appreciate it. Average minds find commonalities and 